ActAppropriation Act No. 1, 2010-11
PrecisAppointment of STEWART BECK as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of India with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Bhutan; TRUDY KERNIGHAN as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Ghana; PERRY CALDERWOOD as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Cape Verde, with residence in Dakar; MARK GWOZDECKY as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Iraq, with residence in Amman; GWYNETH KUTZ as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Paraguay, with residence in Buenos Aires; CAMERON MacKAY as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Nicaragua and the Republic of Honduras, with residence in San José; and MICHAEL SMALL as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Nauru, Papua New Guinea and the Republic of Vanuatu, with residence in Canberra.
